# ============================================================
# ACTIVITY DETAIL POLICY
# ============================================================

status: canonical
layer: policy
domain: detail
subdomain: activity-detail
system: civilization-os
owner: Boss
prepared_by: Zero

purpose:
Defines policy rules for activity detail.

policy_focus:
- work-guidance disclosure boundaries
- blocked-reason disclosure control
- training versus execution detail separation
- revision authority over execution guidance

disclosure_matrix:
- training_guidance: broader internal allowed
- execution_guidance: operator-scoped
- blocked_reason: masked when sensitive
- historical_execution_detail: audit/history mode only

validation_rules:
- execution guidance must not be exposed outside allowed operator scope.
- training detail must not override execution authority.
